OL,3,CBoy, 14, pleads guilty to school
OL,4,Cattack with large serrated knife
OL,6,FA teenager has admitted grave and
OL,7,Fcriminal assault and possession of an
OL,8,Foffensive weapon after a knife attack
OL,9,Fin a Jersey school.
OL,11,FThe 14-year-old boy appeared at the
OL,12,FMagistrate's Court in St Helier on
OL,13,FWednesday morning (11 February), two
OL,14,Fdays after the incident at Haute
OL,15,FVallee School, which left one student
OL,16,Fwith minor injuries.
