OL,4,Cattack with large serrated knife
OL,6,FThe Advocate also described the weapon
OL,7,Fused during the attack at Haute Vallee
OL,8,Fas a large, serrated, rose gold
OL,9,Fkitchen knife.
OL,11,FHe explained that it was brandished by
OL,12,Fthe defendant in the middle of a busy
OL,13,Fcanteen at Monday lunchtime, where
OL,14,Fschool staff quickly tackled the
OL,15,Fteenager to the ground and the knife
OL,16,Fwas taken away.
OL,18,FThe victim, who is a student at the
OL,19,Fschool, suffered a minor hand injury.
