OL,6,FMeanwhile, the defendant will be
OL,7,Fremanded in custody until his next
OL,8,Fscheduled court appearance on Tuesday
OL,9,F17 February.
OL,11,FSeparately, in a letter to parents,
OL,12,Fthe headteacher of Haute Vallee,
OL,13,FStuart Hughes, has sought to offer
OL,14,Freassurance and address concerns over
OL,15,Fsafety, as well as how the situation
OL,16,Fwas handled.
OL,18,FHe wrote: "This was an isolated
OL,19,Fincident, and one that none of us has
OL,20,Fpreviously experienced.
