OL,6,F"Site security has been reviewed, and
OL,7,Fany actions identified will be
OL,8,Faddressed over the coming days and
OL,9,Fweeks."
OL,11,FMr Hughes also apologised for the
OL,12,F"limited" level of initial
OL,13,Fcommunication with parents after the
OL,14,Fincident and stated that he is
OL,15,Fconsidering how UK schools respond to
OL,16,Fthese sorts of incidents for future
OL,17,Fguidance.
